To implement maven project using spring boot 

1) create maven project -> skip archetype selection
2) search -> "spring boot starter maven project" -> Developing your first Spring Boot application -> docs.spring.io
			or 
			org.studyeasy/spring-boot-starter
3) copy parent node from pom :
	<parent>
        <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
        <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-parent</artifactId>
        <version>1.1.4.RELEASE</version>
    </parent>
    
4) Adding classpath dependencies :
	 <dependencies>
	    <dependency>
	        <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
	        <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-web</artifactId>
	    </dependency>
	</dependencies>
    